title: Ep - 58 - Reality Steve & Tammy Knickerbocker
description:
Kate gets Reality Steve to answer never-before-asked Bachelor and Bachelorette questions. He also discusses the new Bachelor Arie and why he had a fall-out with his former friend Jef from the Emily Maynard season. Tammy Knickerbocker from season two of Real Housewives of Orange County talks about being on the show ten years ago and gives updates on her family today. The hilarious writer Matt McConkey reviews 90 Day Fiance: Before 90 Days, a show he had never seen before and now calls riveting television.
